text: FIFA 11 is a 2010 association football simulation video game in Electronic Arts' FIFA series created by EA Canada and published by Electronic Arts. It was released for the Playstation 2, Playstation 3, Playstation Portable, Xbox 360, Wii, Nintendo 3DS, Android, iOS, MacOS and Microsoft Windows.
